title: Taste of the Caribbean
description: Serves meat, veg options available. On Mondays it hosts Meatless Monday from 11am-12am where the dishes are vegan. Sample mains such as jerk chickn slider on gluten-free pretzel bun, mac n cheese quinoa pasta, jackfruit taco with red cabbage claw; bbq cauliflower wings with ranch; green banana fritters. Sample sides such as fried platains; sweet potato fries. For dessert a plantain tart.
